snippet.title: कुमाउँको कथा | Kumaon ko Katha | Herne Katha EP101 | हेर्ने कथा
snippet.description:
बाजुराको डोगडी गाउँदेखि भारतको कुमाउँ-गढवालसम्मको दूरी कति टाढा होला ? 
यो पहाडदेखि त्यो पहाडसम्मको दूरी किलोमिटर र माइलमा मात्र होइन, बाध्यता र भोकमा पनि नापिँदो रहेछ । बाजुरादेखि पिथौरागढ दुई छाक खाना र केही रोटी मात्र टाढा छ । 

नेपालका दुःखका पहाडहरु छाडी, काली तरेर भारतका पहाडहरुमा सुख खोज्न पुग्ने मान्छेहरुले परदेशी कथा बाँचेको पुस्तौं भयो । 
#hernekatha #KuamaonkoKatha
It has been generations since people left the mountains of sorrow in Nepal to find happiness in the mountains of India.

==== Why Herne Katha? ====
People behind Herne Katha spent 15 years of their lives doing journalism. One day they realised the need to tell more beautiful and inspiring stories of people, the real people. 

👀👀👀 Herne Katha 👀👀👀
Herne Katha is a web series produced by Tana Bana Digital in Nepal. We tell stories of people in the format of short documentaries. New episode of Herne Katha is published on  every  alternate Tuesdays (15 days) on YouTube. You can also watch Herne  Katha on Kantipur  Television every Tuesday 6:30 PM.

localized.description:
बाजुराको डोगडी गाउँदेखि भारतको कुमाउँ-गढवालसम्मको दूरी कति टाढा होला ? 
यो पहाडदेखि त्यो पहाडसम्मको दूरी किलोमिटर र माइलमा मात्र होइन, बाध्यता र भोकमा पनि नापिँदो रहेछ । बाजुरादेखि पिथौरागढ दुई छाक खाना र केही रोटी मात्र टाढा छ । 

नेपालका दुःखका पहाडहरु छाडी, काली तरेर भारतका पहाडहरुमा सुख खोज्न पुग्ने मान्छेहरुले परदेशी कथा बाँचेको पुस्तौं भयो ।

snippet.description:
Meri Bassai is one of the longest and most popular Nepali comedy serials with 18 Years of broadcasting. Based on rural lifestyle and lower-middle-class people, the series represents many political and social issues on its episodes with educational comedy flavor. It is aired in Nepal Television at 8:50 PM and in YouTube at 9:30 PM every Tuesday. This show is produced by Media Hub Pvt. Ltd. 

The story is based on the rural lifestyle and lower-middle-class people. The show represents many political as well as social issues on its episodes with educational comedy flavour.

snippet.title: SPIRIT (2023) Full Hindi Dubbed Movie | Prabhas South Indian New Released Full Hindi Movie 2023
snippet.description:
Prabhas's fans have one more reason to rejoice as the actor announced his 25th film today, October 7. His upcoming film, titled Spirit, will be directed by Sandeep Reddy Vanga. The film will be produced on a massive scale by Bhushan Kumar of T-Series. Prabhas is presently shooting for director Prashanth Neel's Salaar and Om Raut's Adipurush. According to reports, Prabhas will be seen in a never-seen-before avatar in the film.

Superstar Prabhas has joined hands with Bhushan Kumar and Sandeep Reddy Vanga for his 25th film titled ‘Spirit’. The details of the film are currently being kept under wraps. However, the movie will be released worldwide in multiple regional and international languages including Hindi, Telugu, Tamil, Malayalam, Kannada, Japanese, Chinese, and Korean. 

Prabhas talked about his 25th movie and expressed excitement for the same. “This is my 25th film and there is no better way to celebrate it. Spirit has a great feel in the story and it’ll be a special film for my fans too,” Prabhas said. He also mentioned that the movie will present him in an ‘avatar’ which fans are eagerly waiting for. “It’s an amazing storyline and I can’t wait to start working on SPIRIT as my fans are eagerly waiting to see me in this avatar for a very long time,” the actor added.

Producer Bhushan Kumar talked about the movie and said the Spirit will be one of his biggest projects. “It’s always been a pleasure working with Prabhas. Spirit will be our fourth film after Saaho, Radhe Shyam and Adipurush and it can’t get bigger and better than this. This will also be our third project with Sandeep who has already delivered the blockbuster Kabir Singh and is now working on Animal. Spirit will not only be one of our biggest projects but it will also be a very special one as it’s Prabhas’ silver jubilee film as well,” he said.

Filmmaker Sandeep expressed excitement for working with Prabhas and said that it’s a pleasure to work with India’s biggest superstar. “Announcing 25th film with India’s biggest superstar will be the biggest news for his fans throughout the world. Working with Prabhas will be a great level of excitement and I’m sure the excitement will be doubled once I start to shoot,” he said.

আমি আমার পরিবারের সাথে সুপার ক্রিয়েটিভ মজার ভিডিও তৈরি করেছি! গোয়েন্দা মা এবং জিনিয়াস ছেলের জন্য কী প্লট টুইস্ট থাকবে? পেটুক মোটা মেয়ে বনিউ খাবার ও ওজন নিয়ে কী গল্প করবে?
আমরা আমাদের পারিবারিক যুদ্ধটি আপনার কল্পনার চেয়ে আরও আশ্চর্যজনক উপায়ে শুরু করব এবং শেষ হবে একেবারেই অপ্রত্যাশিত। সমস্ত ভিডিও আসল এবং আশা করি আপনার জীবনে আনন্দ এবং শিথিলতা আনবে।
আপনি যদি আমাদের মজার কমেডি ভিডিওগুলি পছন্দ করেন তবে সাবস্ক্রাইব 【GuiGe】 এবং ছোট্ট বেলটি চালু করতে ভুলবেন না!

snippet.title: A Soldier's Reaction. #Holiday #shorts
snippet.description:
A military officer attempts to hunt down a terrorist, destroy a terrorist gang and deactivate the sleeper cells under his command.
Cast - Akshay Kumar, Sonakshi Sinha, Freddy Daruwala 
Directed by - A.R. Murugadoss


"Holiday: A Soldier Is Never Off Duty" is a high-octane action film which showcases Akshay Kumar's skills as an action star. The movie boasts of thrilling and intense action sequences, a well-written screenplay, and good performances from the lead actors. The plot of the movie revolves around the life of a soldier on vacation who stumbles upon a terrorist plot and decides to put a stop to it. He has to work with a local police officer and other officials to track down the terrorists and prevent them from carrying out their plan. The film also deals with themes of patriotism and selfless service to the nation. Overall, "Holiday: A Soldier Is Never Off Duty" is a well-crafted action thriller that is sure to keep audiences on the edge of their seats.
#holiday #akshaykumar #sonakshisinha #govinda #freddydaruwala #soldier #shorts

snippet.title: Sudheer Babu's SRIDEVI SODA CENTER (2023) New Released Full Hindi Dubbed Movie | South Movie 2023
snippet.description:
Sudheer Babu's SRIDEVI SODA CENTER (2023) New Released Full Hindi Dubbed Movie | South Movie 2023 | Anandhi 

Presenting New South (Sauth) Indian Movies Dubbed In Hindi 2023 Full (Action Movies 2023) "SRIDEVI SODA CENTER " Starring Sudheer Babu, Anandhi, Pavel Navageethan and Others.

Lighting Suri Babu is an expert in lighting arrangements in his village and aspires to start a shop with the same business. He falls in love with Sridevi whose family business is a Soda center run by her father Sanjeev Rao. Sridevi reciprocates the love but her father disagrees as Suri Babu doesn’t belong to his caste. Suribabu gets tangled in a murder case while a big shot in the village, Kasi becomes another big trouble for him. How Suribabu overcomes the struggle to win his love forms the story.

Produced by: Vijay Chilla, Shashi Devireddy

snippet.description:
आधा शताब्दीअघि तारानाथ शर्मा बैतडी झुलाघाटदेखि हिँडेर डडेल्धुरा पुगेका थिए । घनघस्याको विकट उकालो काट्तै उनले गरेको यात्रा वर्णन विद्यालयमा पुरानो नेपाली विषयको पाठ्यक्रममा पनि समावेश थियो । झन्डै ५५ वर्षपछि ताना शर्माका पैतालाका डोब पछ्याउँदै हामीले पनि घनघस्याको उही उकालो फेरि काट्ने निधो गर्यौं ।
#HerneKatha #Ghanaghasya

Half a century ago, Taranath Sharma walked from Jhulaghat, Baitadi to Dadeldhura. His account of this difficult journey, "Ghanaghasya ko Ukalo Katda" was also included in the older Nepali textbook. 

Now, 55 years later, we decided to take the same journey up the steep hills of Ghanaghasya.

==== Why Herne Katha? ====
People behind Herne Katha spent 15 years of their lives doing journalism. One day they realised the need to tell more beautiful and inspiring stories of people, the real people. 

👀👀👀 Herne Katha 👀👀👀
Herne Katha is a web series produced by Tana Bana Digital in Nepal. We tell stories of people in the format of short documentaries. New episode of Herne Katha is published on  every  alternate Tuesdays (15 days) on YouTube. You can also watch Herne  Katha on Kantipur  Television every Tuesday 6:30 PM.

Have an idea about anything? Anything related to telling people's stories in bold and beautiful style. Share your ideas with us. We love ideas.

snippet.title: Sasta Biig Bosss 2 | Parody | Ashish Chanchlani
snippet.description:
Acv presents the second season of “SASTA BIIG BOSSS”
Chalo pehle brand waalo ka description daalte because PAISAAAA 

WOW Skin Science: ACV Shampoo & Face Wash

Amazon: https://amzn.to/3Xs8zo1 
Flipkart: https://bit.ly/3K06s7I
Nykaa: http://bit.ly/3HVUQ2W

BuyWow: http://bit.ly/3XnDn9y
(Use ASHISHWOW20 for an extra 20% discount)

Haan haan maalum
Hai hume bahut late ho gaya aane mein
Pure 10 nahi nahi 11 mahine lag gaye hume
Lekin tum log ko kya batau aisi fatti padi thi hum log ka kuch aisa project tha jisse plan karte karte karte 6-7 mahine aise nikle hume pata hi nai chala
Fir humne ye saal ka bigg boss dekha aur decide kiya abhi toh hum season 2 banaenge hi kaise bhi
Wo jo project hai jiski baat kar raha hu abhi back burner pe hai but promise hai hum usse kaise bhi aapke saamne laaenge😍

Abhi subah ke 6 baje main ye description bathroom mein likh raha hu seth log toh please deri ke lie maaf kar do baaki tum log hi seth ho mere dhani ho muje maalum hai naraazgi hogi lekin utna hi pyaar bhi karte ho
Chalo abhi video ka Favourite part comment karo aur apna fav dialogue bhi likh lo

Chalo abhi production ka batao is video ka

Actors : wahi sasti team jisme dusre actors ki kami hoti, Akash Dodeja aka jadoo aka gareeb Kunal Chhabhria aka is baar wo kisi ke baap nahi gaya Vibhu Varshney humare video ke super star Simran Dhanwani rotlu pitbul Rohit Sadhwani belt waala anti-singham Tanish Sirwani sandaswala Grishim Nawani dubai waala Akash Jagtap thapad khaane waala Paras rupani playground ka rejected player, Ritesh Sadhwani bhi tha video mein bas ek scene mein kyunki saala gumm ho gaya tha Shivkumar Parthasarathy as humare big-bull Vivek Menon humare super super star as humare host
And ajay bhai jinhone teddy bear ka body double play kiya 

Writer & Director : main hi hu saalo
Editor : wo bhi main hi hu saalo
Background music - Vivek-Abhishek (inka channel dekho bahut talented hai mere bhai log : https://youtube.com/c/VIVEKABHISHEK)
Production Head: Jashan Sirwani & Tanish Sirwani (saara paisa ye log khaa jaate rent aur camera ka😡)
DOP : Ujjawal Gayakwad,Sidharth Kedare
Assistant DOP : Hemendra Singh, Yogi
Gaffer : Ramchandra Vishwakarma
Sound : Satya Narayan
Lights : Golden Lights 
Location : Mania Location
Art : Ravi Kondke and Team
Makeup : Akbar Ali Shaikh and Team
Production : Tushar Manejar and Team
